  "detailed_description": "《LOLI RACING》is a Japanese-style kart racing game, the overall operation difficulty is low and easy to get started, only need to control the direction and drift easy arrive to the finish line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.poster.avif?t=1753685757\" width=480 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.webm?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.mp4?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Players can choose to race alone or invite friends to race together.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/6b220af0c29343b9492276c00db80758.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>The racing tracks you can play have many different themes to choose from, such as shrines and historic site in Japan, urban attractions in Taiwan, or future cities full of high technology.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/622fff4313a438f1470a4c491c78e888.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Players can choose their favorite characters and karts, and the performance and appearance of each kart are different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.poster.avif?t=1753685757\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.webm?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.mp4?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Performance is divided into speed, acceleration, steering, drift, while appearance will vary according to the character's style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/ce54bb960bd7b91ca87c2ce8d83c4a71.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Currently supported game content:<br>▶Single player and multiplayer<br>▶Chat room (lobby only)<br>▶38 tracks<br>▶15 characters and karts<br>▶Two game modes<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/3de1e182cf8afa7a8d7239b518febaf7.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "《LOLI RACING》is a Japanese-style kart racing game, the overall operation difficulty is low and easy to get started, only need to control the direction and drift easy arrive to the finish line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.poster.avif?t=1753685757\" width=480 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.webm?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/a3482226b6bf201c6cd92e7db9b9704e.mp4?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Players can choose to race alone or invite friends to race together.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/6b220af0c29343b9492276c00db80758.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>The racing tracks you can play have many different themes to choose from, such as shrines and historic site in Japan, urban attractions in Taiwan, or future cities full of high technology.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/622fff4313a438f1470a4c491c78e888.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Players can choose their favorite characters and karts, and the performance and appearance of each kart are different.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.poster.avif?t=1753685757\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.webm?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/72931103862e1c0ca581c3fe3c0a9cf6.mp4?t=1753685757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Performance is divided into speed, acceleration, steering, drift, while appearance will vary according to the character's style.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/ce54bb960bd7b91ca87c2ce8d83c4a71.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span><br>Currently supported game content:<br>▶Single player and multiplayer<br>▶Chat room (lobby only)<br>▶38 tracks<br>▶15 characters and karts<br>▶Two game modes<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786360/extras/3de1e182cf8afa7a8d7239b518febaf7.avif?t=1753685757\" width=650 height=370 /></span>",
